article.description: — Gaige Prim scored 23 points and Isiaih Mosley had 14 points and eight rebounds and Missouri State beat Evansville 72-58 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Prim scores 23 to carry Missouri St. past Evansville 72-58
article.linkText: Prim scores 23 to carry Missouri St. past Evansville 72-58
article.story: SPRINGFIELD, Mo. -- — Gaige Prim scored 23 points and Isiaih Mosley had 14 points and eight rebounds and Missouri State beat Evansville 72-58 on Saturday night. Donovan Clay added 11 points and 13 rebounds and Lu'Cye Patterson had 10 points for Missouri State (16-7, 7-3 Missouri Valley Conference). Jawaun Newton scored 18 points, Shamar Givance 17 and Preston Phillips grabbed 12 rebounds for the Purple Aces (5-15, 1-8). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
